Chukwuemeka David Obi (a mụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 6 n'ọnwa Juun n'afọ 2001) bụ onye egwuregwu bọọlụ Naịjirịa na-agbara AFC Fylde bọọlụ.

Oge ọ dị afọ iri na ise na ụbọchị iri asatọ na isii, o mere egwuregwu izizi ya na egwuregwu Football League Trophy maka Bury na 30 Ọgọstụ 2016, na-abịa dịka onye nnọchi anya nkeji iri asatọ na ise na mmeri 4–1 nye Morecambe na-aghọ onye egwuregwu kacha nta na akụkọ ihe mere eme nke klọb ahụ.

N'ọnwa Ọktọba afọ 2016, Obi kwagara Liverpool maka ego isii tinyere arụmọrụ gbakwasara ụkwụ na mgbakwunye.  N'agbanyeghị njem ahụ, ọ pụtaghị na ndepụta ndị otu Liverpool n'okpuru afọ iri na asatọ maka oge 2016-17 ma ọ bụ 2017–18.
N'agbata Septemba na Disemba 2017 ọ pụtara ọtụtụ ugboro maka ndị otu Wigan Athletic's Under 18, na-enye goolu na egwuregwu abụọ. Ná mmalite nke oge 2018–19 ọ nọ na-egosi ọzọ maka Wigan.
N'ọnwa Nọvemba afọ 2018, ọ bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta ọkachamara mbụ ya na Wigan Atletic
Na 1 Febụwarị 2021, Obi hapụrụ Wigan Athletic site na nkwenye.
Na 16 Febụwarị 2021, Obi sonyeere National League North n'akụkụ AFC Fylde na-abụghị nkwekọrịta.
Dịka egwuregwu ọ gbara na 21 Nọvemba 2020.
